== 個人生活 ==
=== 家庭 ===
艾倫·索金的父親為版權律師，母親是教師<ref name="DeJonge-interview">{{cite news |title=Aaron Sorkin Works His Way Through the Crisis |author=Peter De Jonge |date=2001-10-28 |work=The New York Times |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9B01EFD81F3EF93BA15753C1A9679C8B63 |accessdate=2007-01-12}}</ref>，曾祖父則是{{tsl|en|International Ladies' Garment Workers' Union|國際婦女服裝工會}}的創始人之一<ref name="parker-spitzer-cnn">{{cite news |title=Parker/Spitzer Interview Aaron Sorkin (video: 3:05 – father: WWII vet & college on G.I. Bill) |url=http://edition.cnn.com/video/data/2.0/video/us/2010/10/04/parker.spitzer.aaron.sorkin.cnn.html |work = CNN |accessdate=2010-11-13| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20101009092118/http://edition.cnn.com/video/data/2.0/video/us/2010/10/04/parker.spitzer.aaron.sorkin.cnn.html| archivedate= 2010-10-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Awards Watch Roundtable: The Writers part 3 video series |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/gallery/awards-watch-roundtable-writers-43426#3 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2010-11-13 | first = David | last=Simpson | date=2010-11-10 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20101113023014/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/gallery/awards-watch-roundtable-writers-43426| archivedate= 2010-11-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Aaron Sorkin's Four Big Problems With the WGA |url=https://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2010/11/aaron_sorkin_wga.html |work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]] |accessdate=2010-11-13| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20101113071145/http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2010/11/aaron_sorkin_wga.html| archivedate= 2010-11-13}}</ref>。索金有一名哥哥及一名姊姊，哥哥及姊姊後來皆成為律師<ref name="DeJonge-interview" />。

索金與茱莉亞·賓罕於1996年結婚，兩人育有一女，2005年兩人離婚{{efn|1=索金的工作習慣，包括他的用藥史在內，據信都是導致離婚的原因。}}<ref name="Jay Rayner">{{cite news|title=Wing and a prayer|author=Jay Rayner|date=2005-07-10|accessdate=2009-02-19|url=https://www.theguardian.com/stage/2005/jul/10/theatre.foodanddrink|work=The Guardian|location=London|archive-date=2013-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130829064014/http://www.theguardian.com/stage/2005/jul/10/theatre.foodanddrink|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Andrew Gumbel">{{cite news|title=After the West Wing...|author=Andrew Gumbel|work=The Independent|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/after-the-west-wing-511996.html|date=2005-10-22|accessdate=2009-02-19|location=London|archive-date=2009-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090410185653/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/after-the-west-wing-511996.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]在2016年美國總統選舉獲勝後，索金為此撰寫了一封公開信給他的妻女<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/11/aaron-sorkin-donald-trump-president-letter-daughter|title=Read the Letter Aaron Sorkin Wrote His Daughter After Donald Trump Was Elected President|first=Aaron|last=Sorkin|publisher=|access-date=2020-07-19|archive-date=2020-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512202754/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/11/aaron-sorkin-donald-trump-president-letter-daughter|dead-url=no}}</ref>
。

報載索金離婚後曾陸續同演員[[克莉絲汀·錢諾維斯|克莉絲汀·錢諾維斯]]、作家瑪琳·多德（Maureen Dowd）以及演員[[克莉絲汀·戴維斯|克莉絲汀·戴維斯]]等人約會<ref>{{cite book|title=A Little Bit Wicked: Life, Love, and Faith in Stages|author=Kristin Chenoweth|year=2009|isbn=978-1-4165-8055-3|publisher=Simon & Schuster}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Sex & the Single Stiletto |author=Howard Kurtz |date=2005-11-05 |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/11/04/AR2005110401996_pf.html |accessdate=2008-09-25 |archive-date=2008-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080726051110/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/11/04/AR2005110401996_pf.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Kristin Davis, Aaron Sorkin kiss on red carpet, glow with love as they confirm romance | url=http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/kristin-davis-aaron-sorkin-kiss-red-carpet-glowing-love-confirm-romance-article-1.1099956 | date=2012-06-21 | first=Joyce | last=Chen | location=New York | work=Daily News | accessdate=2020-07-19 | archive-date=2012-06-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120625004234/http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/kristin-davis-aaron-sorkin-kiss-red-carpet-glowing-love-confirm-romance-article-1.1099956 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

=== 用藥史 ===
索金早於1987年就有施用大麻和古柯鹼的紀錄，他本人則認為古柯鹼的用途是幫助放鬆<ref name="DeJonge-interview" />。1995年，在女友茱莉亞的建議下，索金曾自願前往{{tsl|en|Hazelden Foundation|海瑟頓基金會}}旗下的勒戒機構，就自己的藥癮尋求幫助。2001年，他的戒藥成功甚至為其贏得了「浴火重生獎」（Phoenix Rising Award），不過，兩個月之後的4月15日，，他就在[[好莱坞伯班克机场|伯班克机场]]因持有[[大麻|大麻]]及[[古柯鹼|古柯鹼]]等藥物被捕，此時他的藥物濫用史始為大眾所知<ref name="DeJonge-interview" /><ref>{{cite news |title=The Crack-Up |author=Michael Cieply |work=Talk |date=2001-09 }}</ref>，當時正直如日中天的《[[白宮風雲|白宮風雲]]》第二季播畢，這起事件為索金的大眾名聲蒙上了陰影。事後，他被強制勒戒，期間並繼續《白宮》的寫作<ref name="CreatorDiverted">{{cite news|title=Aaron Sorkin Says He Used Drugs |agency=Associated Press |url=http://b4a.healthyinterest.net/news/2001_08.html |accessdate=2007-06-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070504064223/http://b4a.healthyinterest.net/news/2001_08.html |archivedate=2007-05-04}}</ref>。

2012年5月13日，索金受邀在母校雪城大學的畢業典禮演說，他表示自己「已經十一年沒有食用古柯鹼」<ref>{{cite web|title=Aaron Sorkin's Commencement Speech - 13 May 2012|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hwvilfPWHYI|work=YouTube|publisher=Google, Inc|accessdate=2013-07-15|author=Syracuse|format=Video upload|date=2012-05-14|archive-date=2013-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130714073241/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hwvilfPWHYI|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 軼事 ==
* 在2000年9月10日的黃金時段艾美獎頒獎典禮上，索金與里克·克里夫蘭（Rick Cleveland）本應共同享有劇情類最佳編劇獎，典禮上卻僅有索金講話，克里夫蘭則沒能在時間內發表感言。《白宮風雲》的部分背景故事是取自克里夫蘭的父親：他是一名韓戰老兵，但後半生都在街頭度過。克里夫蘭以其當事人、劇本共同作者的身分，卻沒有公開發言的機會，引發輿論關注，兩人也公開舌戰了一段時間。最後，這個事件以索金道歉作結<ref>{{cite web |title=In Excelsis Deo |publisher=The West Wing Episode Guide |url=http://www.westwingepguide.com/S1/Episodes/10_IED.html |accessdate=2007-01-17| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070109190429/http://www.westwingepguide.com/S1/Episodes/10_IED.html| archivedate= 2007-01-09}}</ref>。
* 索金對《白宮風雲》的取材和考證頗富自信，他曾批評國廣新聞主播[[湯姆·布羅考|湯姆·布羅考]]的[[乔治·沃克·布什|布希]]訪談（名為《布希時代的白宮：一探真實的白宮西廂》）過於友善，有如「送上情人節禮物一般」。在國廣方面要求下，索金為這番言論公開致歉<ref>{{cite news |title='West Wing' Creator Defends Comments |author=Lynn Elber |date=2002-03-05 |agency=Associated Press |url=http://www.ourmidland.com/news/article/West-Wing-Creator-Defends-Comments-7092823.php |work=Midland Daily News |accessdate=2020-07-19 |archive-date=2016-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111063932/http://www.ourmidland.com/news/article/West-Wing-Creator-Defends-Comments-7092823.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Hollywood's New Radicalism: War, Globalisation and the Movies from Reagan to George W. Bush |url=https://archive.org/details/hollywoodsnewrad00dick |first=Ben |last=Dickenson |date=2006-03-03 |publisher=I. B. Tauris |pages=[https://archive.org/details/hollywoodsnewrad00dick/page/n127 111]–112 |isbn=978-1-84511-103-8}}</ref>。

